{"id":641205,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/【立此存照】动物森友会全网下架/","date":"2020-04-10T09:54:38Z","modified":"2020-04-11T09:50:17Z","title":"【立此存照】“动物森友会”实体卡全网下架 网友评：中国速度","content":"<p>4月10日，有网民发现近期全球大火的任天堂nintendo switch游戏《动物森友会》在中国各网络平台“全网下架”，全面禁止电商平台销售游戏的实体卡带。（该游戏并无“国行版本”，中国玩家需要购买数字版本或实体卡带运行游戏）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOrmxUU4AAJQrL.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641217\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOrmxUU4AAJQrL.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"656\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOrmxUU4AAJQrL.jpg 686w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOrmxUU4AAJQrL-229x300.jpg 229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>目前淘宝平台已无法检索到“动物森友会实体卡”的有关内容，而部分周边产品仍可搜到。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn2o0d5j20pv0i274p-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641207\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn2o0d5j20pv0i274p-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn2o0d5j20pv0i274p-1.jpg 931w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn2o0d5j20pv0i274p-1-300x209.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn2o0d5j20pv0i274p-1-768x536.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641208\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"328\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x.jpg 1647w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x-300x197.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x-1024x671.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x-768x504.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x-1536x1007.jpg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4ad9ebb8ly1gdohn53srvj219r0u0u0x-1080x708.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>《集合啦！动物森友会》（日版名：あつまれ どうぶつの森，英文版名：Animal Crossing: New Horizons，又译作“动物森友会：新地平线”）是一款由任天堂企划制作本部开发并由任天堂发行在任天堂Switch上的生活模拟游戏。本作是动物森友会系列的第7款作品。游戏上市后获得了极大的成功，多个评论赞誉游戏的设计，认为《集合啦！动物森友会》成功塑造了一个活生生的世界。在日本，游戏发售3天共售出超过188万套。   来源：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E5%95%A6%EF%BC%81%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E6%A3%AE%E5%8F%8B%E6%9C%83\">维基百科</a></p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Animal_Crossing_New_Horizons.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-641209\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Animal_Crossing_New_Horizons.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"248\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Animal_Crossing_New_Horizons.png 248w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/Animal_Crossing_New_Horizons-185x300.png 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 248px) 100vw, 248px\" /></a></p>\n<p>动物森友会赋予了玩家高度的创作自主性，例如玩家可以在自己的无人岛上进行自由的贴图、摆设、家具、服装设计，于是有不少玩家创作出“恶搞习近平”、“光复香港时代革命”、“悼念李文亮”等内容，并引起了互联网上的广泛传播。</p>\n<p>目前互联网上普遍的猜测认为，动物之森下架原因与此类时政内容创作有关。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_641210\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5e8ff678de7b0.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641210\" class=\"wp-image-641210\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5e8ff678de7b0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5e8ff678de7b0.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5e8ff678de7b0-300x223.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641210\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">网传下架通知</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_641218\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOq9tZUMAEuyGw.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-641218\" class=\"wp-image-641218\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOq9tZUMAEuyGw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOq9tZUMAEuyGw.jpg 425w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOq9tZUMAEuyGw-300x248.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-641218\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">一些卖家不得已“改头换面”</p></div>\n<p><strong>以下为部分动森玩家的自由创作：</strong></p>\n<p>讽刺武汉肺炎：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/46S3DQY7I7HETEKFGSSVHYCVVY.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641211\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/46S3DQY7I7HETEKFGSSVHYCVVY.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/46S3DQY7I7HETEKFGSSVHYCVVY.jpg 802w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/46S3DQY7I7HETEKFGSSVHYCVVY-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/46S3DQY7I7HETEKFGSSVHYCVVY-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>缅怀李文亮医生：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-35.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640069\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-35.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-35.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/1-35-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641270\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5617-100x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5617-100x300.jpg 100w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5617-341x1024.jpg 341w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5617-512x1536.jpg 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5617.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>讽刺习近平：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/sUnfZm.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641213\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/sUnfZm.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"269\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/sUnfZm.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/sUnfZm-300x162.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/sUnfZm-1024x552.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/sUnfZm-768x414.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOTXSRUMAAYESG.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641219\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOTXSRUMAAYESG.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOTXSRUMAAYESG.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOTXSRUMAAYESG-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/38jEtvf.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641224\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/38jEtvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/38jEtvf.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/38jEtvf-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/38jEtvf-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/38jEtvf-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641212\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森.jpg 1485w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森-300x168.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森-768x431.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/动森-1080x606.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/animaltitle-770x439_c.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641225\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/animaltitle-770x439_c.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/animaltitle-770x439_c.png 770w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/animaltitle-770x439_c-300x171.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/animaltitle-770x439_c-768x438.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641237\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVO_Th6UEAcsa-E-1080x608.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“光复香港时代革命”：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVNtfFqVAAMatL8.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641216\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVNtfFqVAAMatL8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVNtfFqVAAMatL8.png 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVNtfFqVAAMatL8-300x229.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVORuESUwAEwAbK.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641220\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVORuESUwAEwAbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVORuESUwAEwAbK.jpg 360w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVORuESUwAEwAbK-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/fung.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641221\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/fung.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/fung.jpg 810w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/fung-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/fung-768x431.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUF1sq2UMAAo1Ll.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641222\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUF1sq2UMAAo1Ll.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"242\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUF1sq2UMAAo1Ll.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUF1sq2UMAAo1Ll-300x145.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUF1sq2UMAAo1Ll-768x371.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUALbuyXYAU5dFZ.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641226\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUALbuyXYAU5dFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUALbuyXYAU5dFZ.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EUALbuyXYAU5dFZ-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>漫画家 @badiucao 的画作“连侬墙旗”也被玩家加入了游戏之中：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">早说会下架啦 <a href=\"https://t.co/DDNB8sN6TB\">https://t.co/DDNB8sN6TB</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草麻酱🀄️ Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1248483496172982272?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>在“动物森友会”下架之后，黄之锋在twitter表示自己受到了大量中国玩家的攻击，他反问攻击者为什么你们不是责怪自己的政府而是责怪我~</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Oh no, Xi Jinping banned <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AnimalCrossing?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#AnimalCrossing</a> in China (apparently because I play it), and these angry gamers are blaming me everywhere instead of blaming their own government lol 🤨🎮🎮 <a href=\"https://t.co/FdzObiFAyk\">pic.twitter.com/FdzObiFAyk</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Joshua Wong 黃之鋒 😷 (@joshuawongcf) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1248494508146221058?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>其中，有一些中国玩家将“动物森友会”的下架原因归咎于黄之锋号召在游戏中“政治恶搞”：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/92298300_2913815485377607_7963777567683510272_n.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-641223\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/92298300_2913815485377607_7963777567683510272_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"454\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/92298300_2913815485377607_7963777567683510272_n.jpg 454w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/92298300_2913815485377607_7963777567683510272_n-142x300.jpg 142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" /></a></p>\n<p>当然，也有中国玩家对“动物森友会”的下架进行了辛辣的讽刺：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOtatbU0AA-luE.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641215\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOtatbU0AA-luE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOtatbU0AA-luE.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVOtatbU0AA-luE-300x259.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVObFs9U4AA567F.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641214\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVObFs9U4AA567F.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"444\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVObFs9U4AA567F.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/EVObFs9U4AA567F-300x266.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641272\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5803-300x271.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"451\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5803-300x271.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5803-1024x925.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5803-768x693.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5803-1080x975.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/IMG_5803.jpg 1122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑摘自网友评论：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>@taocomic：动物森友会，任天堂switch游戏，在中国全面下架，原因是无法对游戏里玩家创建的内容进行审查，出现大量“光复香港”“台湾独立”以及侮辱维尼熊之类的内容。我被封杀也是同理。可怜的同胞，被蒙住双眼，看到的一切都必须被过滤。可恨的是，很多玩家不敢骂蒙他眼的奴隶主，却骂争自由的台蛙港废汉奸…够贱</p>\n<p>@nxw****MaZNP：连个游戏都害怕，啧啧啧</p>\n<p>@Lad****u5：讓我想到有次在b站看日本綜藝節目有個搞笑藝人模仿安倍，旁邊藝人都在笑，就有ㄧ些彈幕說日本人膽子真大，然後就有彈幕說因為安倍不得民心所以被群嘲，中國領導做得好⋯</p>\n<p>@tol****cyly：没有把购买过的玩家骨灰扬了就是我党最大的仁慈。</p>\n<p>@xin****604：粉蛆太监不怪把它阉割的皇帝，反而怪起了卖刀的铁匠。</p>\n<p>@jQym****XIPW：疯狂加速咯，维尼开心就好。</p>\n<p>@lo****oo：只怪党国自身G点太多动不动就高潮，和游戏没啥关系。</p>\n<p>@Sir****noy：上联：强奸幼女，多次报案无结果。下联：动森反中，立马全网给下架。横批：中国速度。</p>\n<p>@Ser****ndle：话说回来动森本来就是自由度较高的游戏，人家在游戏里做什么你都管不到。只能怪你有一个游戏都不让你好好玩的政府。</p>\n<p>@Soli****ola：“国家面前无游戏，民族大义赛动森“、”任天堂你想要恰我们中国的烂钱就先把废青清洗干净“、”虚拟世界不是法外之地“、”创作可以，夹带私货NMSL“、”不要被带了节奏去骂ZF“，”我首先是一个中国人，然后才是一名玩家“。草稿我都拟好了。</p>\n<p>@yu****ao：大概知道为什么下架动森卡带了，比这悲哀的是有人说不应该在游戏里搞政治。朋友，这不是游戏里搞政治，这是政治搞你，政治无处不在。</p>\n<p>@19****4obli：就算按“废青捣乱”这个逻辑，那不去惩罚“废青”，却反过来惩罚你们这些爱国者不准玩游戏，那你们就没有对决策的公平性合理性有一丁点疑问么？</p>\n<p>@bear****ation：因为你家政府不喜欢某种言论，所以全世界的玩家都不能在任何国家出品的游戏（或其他文化产品）里表达这些言论，否则就要为你家政府不让你们玩这些游戏负责任。这么觉得的人我觉得你们再仔细想想这个逻辑有问题没。</p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,38962,39484],"tags":[13222,40199,18705,40198,40214,9249,9283,25890]}